data.description: Rare opportunity for a 4 br townhome nestled on the golf course!  Freshly painted interior and new flooring throughout enhance the spacious living areas.  The main level boasts an open dining and family room, a bright front living room and convenient half bath and laundry.  Upstairs, indulge in a primary suite with attached covered patio along with 3 additional bedrooms and a second full bath.  Outside, a spacious 1-car garage offers plenty of extra room for tools, toys or storage.  Completing the package are the Country Club Estates amenities including a golf course, clubhouse, pool, hot tub and fitness facilities.  Don?t miss this unique and affordable 4 bedroom home!
